    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, budget-friendly transportation option. While the engine and transmission are functional and the car remains drivable, there are noticeable signs of wear including some exterior scratches, minor dings, and interior upholstery that shows its age. It has been used regularly and may require some upcoming minor maintenance, but it still has plenty of life left for a buyer looking for a practical deal.",
