    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained to ensure a reliable driving experience. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts precisely, making it a dependable choice for any driver. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of regular use, such as small surface scratches or light wear on the upholstery, the car remains very clean and structurally sound. It is a solid, honest vehicle that performs exactly as it should.",
